Registration Form

A simple and responsive registration form built with HTML5 and CSS3.
This project is part of Phase 1 – Week 2 Mini Projects.

🚀 Features

Semantic HTML structure (header, main, footer)

Responsive design with Flexbox and max-width container

Form validation with required, minlength, and regex pattern checks

Password requirements guide (uppercase, lowercase, number, min 8 characters)

Clean and modern UI with shadows, rounded corners, and hover effects

Live Demo

https://davidokoni09.github.io/Registration-form/

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5 for structure

CSS3 for styling & layout
